1811 /* add_location */
1817 void add_location(double point, location ** p_location)
1818 {
1819  location * current = *p_location;
1820  location * tmp = NULL;
1821  location * newlocation = NULL;
1822  int found = 0;
1823 
1824  while(found == 0)
1825  {
1826  if(current == NULL) found = 1;
1827  else if(point > current->point) found = 1;
1828  else
1829  {
1830  tmp = current;
1831  current = current->next;
1832  }
1833  }
1834 
1835  newlocation = (location *)malloc(sizeof(location));
1836  CHECK_POINTER(newlocation);
1837  if(tmp)
1838  {
1839  tmp->next = newlocation;
1840  }
1841  else
1842  {
1843  *p_location = newlocation;
1844  }
1845 
1846  newlocation->next = current;
1847  newlocation->point = point;
1848 }

2371 void transition_firm_agent(xmachine_memory_firm_holder * tmp, xmachine_memory_firm_state * from_state, xmachine_memory_firm_state * to_state)
2372 {
2373  if(tmp->prev == NULL) from_state->agents = tmp->next;
2374  else tmp->prev->next = tmp->next;
2375  if(tmp->next != NULL) tmp->next->prev = tmp->prev;
2376 
2377  add_firm_agent_internal(tmp->agent, to_state);
2378  free(tmp);
2379 }

2381 void add_firm_agent_internal(xmachine_memory_firm * agent, xmachine_memory_firm_state * state)
2382 {
2383  xmachine_memory_firm_holder * current = (xmachine_memory_firm_holder *)malloc(sizeof(xmachine_memory_firm_holder));
2384  CHECK_POINTER(current);
2385 
2386  current->next = state->agents;
2387  current->prev = NULL;
2388  state->agents = current;
2389  if(current->next != NULL) current->next->prev = current;
2390  current->agent = agent;
2391 
2392  state->count++;
2393 
2394 }
